ck new customization items to make your alien even more stylish</li></ul></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cozy and Comforting Environment</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/Turntable.gif?t=1726428005\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Choose Your Own Focus Music</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Curated playlists are included<br></li><li>Import your own music and create custom playlist </li></ul></li><li><strong>Delicate and Versatile Lighting</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The light from the window will reflect your local time and change smoothly as time passes.<br></li><li> Light intensity will adjust based on your settings, including curtain closure or indoor lighting preferences.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Friendly Visitors</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Alpha Centauri is home to cat-like native species, Nyan. They will visit your home from time to time. Greet them and fill your Nyan dictionary. </li></ul></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">And More</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Built-in &quot;Always on Top&quot; setting<br></li><li>Low memory usage; runs well with other applications</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome Home","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2965050/a8082247bd372111b5f89bfb6382fa836265b348.jpg"},{"name":"Tomato Is Green","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2965050/978e327a63d13dea684a33a6d9a4ac904fab5ace.jpg"},{"name":"Tomato Ripe!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2965050/7c9ef9f40a026b09439c2a3b56d34d8cd35b0d03.jpg"},{"name":"LOVING IT","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2965050/949fe1e24694545d439248ff846d2f70c9163dc5.jpg"},{"name":"Promise Kept","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2965050/91e31d7ef5e8d154af476d95b28d9572fe61c